{"tid":855581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Apple用戶被盜】支付寶建議 調低免密碼支付額度","createTime":"2018-10-10T06:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T08:37:19.000Z","uid":56533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e350a559d7a11724a832aeb53317beca8064a31","tid":855581,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539145403_8575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539145403_8575.jpg&h=8c1361a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地日前有多個Apple用戶帳號在「免密碼支付」功能下遭盜用，綁定的「支付寶」被自動扣數，支付寶官方微博今日（10日）凌晨發佈安全提示，指支付寶多次聯繫Apple提升安全防範水平，故建議用戶將「免密碼支付」額度調低。<br />\n<br />\n內地Apple用戶賬戶被盜，由於綁定的第三方支付平台「支付寶」，兼開啟了「免密碼支付」，賬戶由此造成資金損失，最高者逾萬元。支付寶表示，已聯繫Apple盡快找出被盜原因。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶於安全提示中提及，Apple公司未完全解決問題前，無論用戶的Apple ID綁定哪種支付方式（包括支付寶、微信支付或信用卡）都可能出現資金損失風險。用戶在確保方便的前提下，可選擇調低Apple Pay「免密碼支付」的額度，以最大限度保護賬戶資金安全。<br />\n<br />\nApple Pay可不設置限額，「免密碼支付」額度有200/500/1000/1500元等，最低額度是200元。對於支付寶的安全提示，有網民認為建議不負責任，因為將責任全卸給Apple公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181010/58777263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58777263&d=vnaf3LLGtUYd2jTxRifVD%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3ff347f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58777263&h=01588f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181010/58777263</a>"},{"pid":"85c449ab3803cabc3f804a65918aac51267e51ab","tid":855581,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"支付寶於安全提示中提及，Apple公司未完全解決問題前<br />\n<br />\n幾絕下喎"},{"pid":"6959aa3eb3afe30b83d5a4f25cc9a0fc04a5518f","tid":855581,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"無優惠的話，有無香港人會長期用支那寶？"},{"pid":"ee9ee5d033b703c34b5cc12a67f5566a97da0410","tid":855581,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"又唔見其他人有事  係得支那寶有問題又屈蘋果"},{"pid":"3a1a22438732ed36769551d61c443c0f37371856","tid":855581,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"索性唔用咪得囉屌"},{"pid":"4deaf1e2de2e218bad0bc48816c06165d90c2a61","tid":855581,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}